<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>Sog Ľinchlarim sado bo Ľlib</title>
<aka>Najotkor</aka>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Sog Ľinchlarim sado bo Ľlib,
 Uchib borsin samolarga.
 Tuyg Ľularim nido bo Ľlib,
 Aylansaydi sanolarga.

[V2]
 Meni yangi ijod qilgan,
 Ijodkorim, san ľatkorim.
 Ibrohimga avlod qilgan,
 Xaloskorim, Najotkorim.

[V3]
 Sen hammadan ulug Ľimsan,
 Mangulikka chorlagan
 Yurar yo Ľlim, yo Ľrig Ľimsan,
 Hayotimda porlagan.

[V4]
 Gunohimga to Ľlab tovon,
 Qilib bo Ľlding O Ľz ishingni.
 Bilmas edim men notavon,
 Meni cheksiz sevishingni.

[V5]
 Masih, Noming yuksalib,
 Ibrat olay so Ľzlaringdan.
 Men ham xochim ko Ľtarib,
 Yuray endi izlaringdan.

[V6]
 Sen hammadan ulug Ľimsan,
 Mangulikka chorlagan
 Yurar yo Ľlim, yo Ľrig Ľimsan,
 Hayotimda porlagan</lyrics>
</song>